name: Catch The Chicken Eggs
description:
Let's play amazing arcade game. Your job is catch the colourful eggs in the basket and avoid bomb. you need to move basket from left to right. And catch the maximum eggs and create your best score. You have 5 lives for the game score.

Features:
=======
- Easy game play.
- There are 5 lives.
- Colourful graphics.
- Endless game play.
- Supported IOS11.

So are you ready for beat me? Download Now...
